SELECT t.booking_id, t.booking_date, t.cancellation_status, t.confirmed, t.created_at, t.guests, t.nights, t.rating, t.reminder_sent, t.review, t."StartDate", t.status, t.total_price, t.updated_at, t.user_id, t.user_id0, t.created_at0, t.email, t."GoogleId", t.name, t.password, t."Picture", t.role, t0.booking_id, t0.destination_id, t0.destination_id0, t0.city, t0.country, t0.created_at, t0.description, t0.image_url, t0.latitude, t0.longitude, t0.name, t0.price
FROM (
    SELECT b.booking_id, b.booking_date, b.cancellation_status, b.confirmed, b.created_at, b.guests, b.nights, b.rating, b.reminder_sent, b.review, b."StartDate", b.status, b.total_price, b.updated_at, b.user_id, u.user_id AS user_id0, u.created_at AS created_at0, u.email, u."GoogleId", u.name, u.password, u."Picture", u.role
    FROM bookings AS b
    INNER JOIN users AS u ON b.user_id = u.user_id
    WHERE b.booking_id = @__bookingId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT b0.booking_id, b0.destination_id, d.destination_id AS destination_id0, d.city, d.country, d.created_at, d.description, d.image_url, d.latitude, d.longitude, d.name, d.price
    FROM booking_destinations AS b0
    INNER JOIN destinations AS d ON b0.destination_id = d.destination_id
) AS t0 ON t.booking_id = t0.booking_id
ORDER BY t.booking_id, t.user_id0, t0.booking_id, t0.destination_id
